Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Hematoma' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Pelvis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thigh' checkbox is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled

And 'T1w signal' slide bar is enabled
And 'T2w signal' slide bar is enabled

And 'Hyperacute' radio button is enabled
And 'Acute' radio button is enabled
And 'Subacute' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic, organized' radio button is enabled

And 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pelvis' checkbox
Then 'Ventral' checkbox is enabled
And 'Medial' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dorsal' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Thigh' checkbox
Then 'Ventral' checkbox is enabled
And 'Medial' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dorsal' checkbox is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 500 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled
When I enter any value from 1 to 500 in '2nd plane' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled

When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled
